{"word":"G4375 - προσφιλής - prosphilḗs - pros-fee-lace' - Lovely","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">προσφιλής</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">prosphilḗs</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">pros-fee-lace'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Lovely</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"அன்புள்ள - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"acceptable, pleasing, lovely"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From a presumed compound of <a href=\"#/G4314 - πρός - prós - pros/4314\">G4314</a> and <a href=\"#/G5368 - φιλέω - philéō - fil-eh'-o/5368\">G5368</a>; <i>friendly towards</i>, that is, <i>acceptable:</i> - lovely.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}